title: Thom Hartmann Program with Mike Papantonio - January 08 2014
description:
January 08, 2014
The Thom Hartmann Program 

In for Thom today, please welcome attorney Mike Papantonio, Ring of Fire Radio

Hour One: Unemployment benefit cuts - Sam Seder, Ring of Fire Radio / Majority.fm

Hour Two: JP Morgan/Madoff settlement - James Kauffman, Levin Law / Plus, polarization works for the wealthy - Joshua Holland, Moyers & Company

Hour Three: What Congress Can Do to Help Fight Poverty - Zoe Carpenter, The Nation / A Physician's Apology - Dr. Thomas Schneider
